    "updated_at": "2014-03-11T19:01:18Z",
    "body": "I kind of got this working by setting the `http_proxy` environment variable (lower case), but then I got a bunch of node exceptions coming out of the `request` library. I worked around these by modifying some of the source for that library. Regardless, I think I've figured out a reliable way to proxy stuff, so I'll close this.\n"
